73014\" href=\"/food/0/27164636\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/74498000/jpg/_74498469_noodles_cropped.jpg\" alt=\"Szechuan noodles\" />Sweet and spicy</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h3>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Chinese food&#039;s return to authenticity pays off \t\r\n\t\t\t\t  <span id=\"dna-comment-count___CPS__27164636\" class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-comment comment-count\"></span></p>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\r\n\t \r\n\t\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n  \t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t<!-- Non specific version -->\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t<li class=\"medium-image\">\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\" feature-header\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1398996038395\" href=\"/food/0/27198065\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/74519000/jpg/_74519233_img_1559.jpg\" alt=\"Party Boy bagel\" />Pop-up spirit</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h3>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Why the West Country&#039;s food is making waves \t\r\n\t\t\t\t  <span id=\"dna-comment-count___CPS__27198065\" class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-comment comment-count\"></span></p>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<hr />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t<li class=\"medium-image\">\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\" feature-header\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1398246461494\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/scones_1285\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/74391000/jpg/_74391450_scones_1285_16x9.jpg\" alt=\"Scones\" />Super scones</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h3>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Perfect with dried fruit or cinnamon then slather on the jam \t\r\n\t\t\t\t  <span id=\"dna-comment-count___CPS__27126592\" class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-comment comment-count\"></span></p>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<hr />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t<li class=\"medium-image\">\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\r\